		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Inside the house, there's a small girl&#xD;&#xA;- Speak to the girl there&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Bookmark for the house: larian://bookmark?name=CTY_JaheirasHouse&amp;mod=GustavDev&amp;level=CTY_Main_A&amp;camPos=-198.180267;36.128036;-47.551403&amp;camTarget=-198.939575;35.720970;-47.043709" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="48" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Jaheira's granddaughter that is inside - she's earnest and friendly.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Her clue that she supplies the player with is to do with how to access Jaheira's hidden items in the basement - that puzzle is 4 orbs you hit with different spells to produce little platforms and jump across to get to her personal gear." />
